    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be fully aware of its significant issues before considering a purchase. The exterior shows heavy wear including rust, dents, and paint damage that go well beyond cosmetic concerns. Mechanically, the car has known problems that will require substantial repair work; it is not in reliable daily-driver condition and may need immediate attention from a qualified mechanic. This listing is best suited for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle, parts sourcing, or those with mechanical expertise who can restore it \u2014 it is priced accordingly to reflect its current state.",
